lead_paragraph: Top-ranked Lydia Ko shot a 3-under 69 on Wednesday in the Coates Golf Championship in her first round of the season, leaving her four strokes behind leader Ha Na Jang.

headline.print_headline: Lydia Ko Opens Season, 4 Shots Behind Ha Na Jang in Ocala
